(Forsskål in Niebuhr 1775)
</taxonomicName>
—Bloodspot squirrelfish (
<figureCitation id="05E5AECD8057FFF4E96DCAD01D040B6E" box="[1030,1113,1273,1298]" captionStart="FIGURE 27" captionStartId="82.[151,250,1397,1419]" captionTargetBox="[151,1437,411,1375]" captionTargetId="figure@82.[151,1437,411,1375]" captionTargetPageId="82" captionText="FIGURE 27. Myripristis violacea Bleeker 1851 (lower) and Neoniphon sammara (Forsskål in Niebuhr 1775) (upper), Lissenung Island, Kavieng District, 5 m depth, 6 July 2011 (underwater photograph: Dean Tully)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2988391/files/figure.png" pageId="83" pageNumber="84">Fig. 27</figureCitation>
